import {
  Box,
  TextField,
  MenuItem,
  FormControl,
  Typography,
  LoadingButton,
} from "@mui/material";

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        flexWrap: "wrap",
        width: "auto",
        border: "0.1px solid black",
      }}
      mt={12}
      ml="auto"
      mr="auto"
      p={5}
    >
      <Typography variant="h3">Creare cont</Typography>
      <Box component="form" noValidate autoComplete="off">
        <FormControl>
          <TextField type="text" label="Nume" variant="outlined" size="small" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            type="email"
            label="Email"
            variant="outlined"
            size="small"
          />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            type="password"
            label="Parolă"
            variant="outlined"
            size="small"
          />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            type="password"
            label="Confirmare parolă"
            variant="outlined"
            size="small"
          />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            label="Sex"
            variant="outlined"
            select
            sx={{ width: 75 }}
            value=""
            size="small"
          >
            <MenuItem value=""></MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="m">M</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="f">F</MenuItem>
          </TextField>
        </FormControl>
      </Box>
      <LoadingButton>Înregistrare</LoadingButton>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
